  "description": "<a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540357/\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/ce5ed9ee56f840f6a6052630542f0f57.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tAnne Hathaway, Rachel Zoe, and Kate Beckinsale hit the red carpet for LA retailer Elyse Walker's annual Pink Party in Santa Monica, CA, on Saturday night.</p>\n<p>\n\tAnne, who hosted the event, looked stunning in a short pink J.Mendel dress and flashed her <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/megawatt\" target=\"_blank\">megawatt</a> smile while posing for photos.</p>\n<p>\n\tIt's been a while since we've seen Anne out and about, and she's kept a pretty low profile since attending the Met Gala back in May. The Oscar-winning actress recently began filming the Christopher Nolan sci-fi thrill Interstellar with Jessica Chastain and Matthew McConaughey, and has likely been spending her downtime with husband Adam Schulman &mdash; the couple celebrated their first wedding anniversary late last month.<br />\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/0af3df5d27424959a2f31e5d4c988f0c.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>沪江娱乐</strong>：安妮&middot;海瑟薇，瑞秋&middot;佐伊和凯特&middot;贝金赛尔当地时间周六晚出现在圣莫妮卡举办的Pink Party。安妮同时也是此次活动的主持人.一身粉色短裙亮相的安妮拍照时露出了招牌笑容。自五月参加Met Gala后，我们很久没有在公众场合看到过安妮。这位奥斯卡最佳女配角最近正在和杰西卡&middot;查斯坦和马修&middot;麦康纳一起出演诺兰的星际科幻片。在休息时间，安妮更喜欢和丈夫亚当在一起度过&mdash;&mdash;上月，他们一起庆祝了结婚一周年纪念日。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540357/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540357\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539727/\">20个你应该了解的高频英语习语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540077/\">每天新开始：早上问自己的10个问题</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p535763/\">魔鬼口语1000句（80）：磨蹭什么呢</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539422/\">今日公开课推荐：打造完美口语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540213/\">男子花十万美元整容成贾斯汀&bull;比伯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539741/\">前智能时代：以前等人时做的21件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540177/\">谢耳朵首次携男友公开亮相</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540230/\">凯特王妃产后迅速瘦身 玩排球秀蛮腰</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539327/\">好朋友在身边：如何做个真正的朋友</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
